subject: NCAA Basketball Tournament

College Athletics
lead_paragraph: No matter the location, no matter the style, No. 2 Kansas keeps showing it is the premier basketball program in the state. And that may help the Jayhawks become a No. 1 seed in the N.C.A.A. tournament.
